    <entry>
      <title>hexo博客搭建</title>
      <link href="/2022/03/10/hexo%E5%8D%9A%E5%AE%A2%E6%90%AD%E5%BB%BA/"/>
      <url>/2022/03/10/hexo%E5%8D%9A%E5%AE%A2%E6%90%AD%E5%BB%BA/</url>
      
        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h1 id="前言"><a href="#前言" class="headerlink" title="前言"></a>前言</h1><div class="note blue icon simple"><i class="note-icon fas fa-bullhorn"></i><p><strong>Hexo 是一个快速、简洁且高效的博客框架。Hexo 使用 Markdown（或其他渲染引擎）解析文章，在几秒内，即可利用靓丽的主题生成静态网页。</strong></p></div><h1 id="准备工作"><a href="#准备工作" class="headerlink" title="准备工作"></a>准备工作</h1><div class="note purple icon disabled"><i class="note-icon fas fa-bullhorn"></i><p><a class="btn-beautify orange outline" href="https://git-scm.com/downloads" title="安装git"><i class="far fa-hand-point-right"></i><span>安装git</span></a><br><a class="btn-beautify orange outline larger" href="https://nodejs.org/en/" title="安装nodejs"><i class="far fa-hand-point-right"></i><span>安装nodejs</span></a></p></div><h2 id="安装情况"><a href="#安装情况" class="headerlink" title="安装情况"></a>安装情况</h2><div class="note blue icon simple"><i class="note-icon fas fa-bullhorn"></i><p><strong>打开<mark class="hl-label orange">CMD命令</mark> 下查看</strong></p></div><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">node -v (version)     <span class="string">&quot;提示版本信息 v16.14.0&quot;</span></span><br><span class="line">npm -v (version)      <span class="string">&quot;提示版本信息 8.5.3&quot;</span></span><br><span class="line">git --version         <span class="string">&quot;版本相关信息&quot;</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h2 id="环境配置"><a href="#环境配置" class="headerlink" title="环境配置"></a>环境配置</h2><div class="note blue icon flat"><i class="note-icon fas fa-bullhorn"></i><p><strong>说明：这里的环境配置主要配置的是npm安装的全局模块所在的路径，以及缓存cache的路径，之所以要配置，是因为以后在执行类似：npm install express [-g] (后面的可选参数-g，g代表global全局安装的意思)的安装命令时，会将安装的模块安装到【C:\Users\用户名\AppData\Roaming\npm】路径中，占用C盘。——个人需要</strong></p></div><ul><li><strong>在nodejs安装目录下创建 <strong>node_cache</strong> 和 <strong>node_global</strong> 两个文件夹</strong></li></ul><p><img src="/2022/03/10/hexo%E5%8D%9A%E5%AE%A2%E6%90%AD%E5%BB%BA/img/hj.png"></p><h2 id="DOS命令"><a href="#DOS命令" class="headerlink" title="DOS命令"></a>DOS命令</h2><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">npm config <span class="built_in">set</span> prefix <span class="string">&quot;D:\nodejs\node_global&quot;</span>   (自己的文件路径)</span><br><span class="line">npm config <span class="built_in">set</span> cache <span class="string">&quot;D:\nodejs\node_cache&quot;</span>     (自己的文件路径)</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h2 id="配置环境变量-PATH"><a href="#配置环境变量-PATH" class="headerlink" title="配置环境变量 PATH"></a>配置环境变量 PATH</h2><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">【用户变量】编辑PATH变量  路径 <span class="string">&quot;D:\nodejs\node_global&quot;</span>  (自己的文件路径)</span><br><span class="line">【系统变量】新建NODE_PATH 系统变量  路径 <span class="string">&quot;D:\nodejs\node_global\node_modules&quot;</span>  (node_modules 没有也没有关系)</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><hr><h1 id="安装-hexo-博客框架"><a href="#安装-hexo-博客框架" class="headerlink" title="安装 hexo 博客框架"></a>安装 <a href="https://hexo.io/zh-cn/">hexo</a> 博客框架</h1><blockquote><ul><li><strong>接下来的操作命令 皆在Git Bash下进行 (权限问题，可用管理员打开)</strong></li><li><strong>使用npm 安装 hexo</strong></li></ul></blockquote><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">npm install -g hexo-cli</span><br><span class="line">hexo -v    <span class="string">&quot;查看 hexo 安装版本信息&quot;</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><blockquote><ul><li>新建一个指定路径下你要生成博客相关文件的目录–blog</li></ul></blockquote><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">hexo init  <span class="string">&quot;当前blog文件夹中生成，搭建过程中有问题，操作不当等 即可删除此文件夹&quot;</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h2 id="启动hexo博客服务"><a href="#启动hexo博客服务" class="headerlink" title="启动hexo博客服务"></a>启动hexo博客服务</h2><ul><li><strong>在blog路径下执行，后续修改和配置文件等都需要执行一下操作</strong></li></ul><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">hexo cl (clean)    <span class="string">&quot;清除缓存文件&quot;</span></span><br><span class="line">hexo g (generate) <span class="string">&quot;生成静态文件&quot;</span></span><br><span class="line">hexo s (server)   <span class="string">&quot;启动服务&quot;</span></span><br><span class="line">hexo clean &amp;&amp; hexo generate &amp;&amp; hexo server   <span class="string">&quot;一键执行&quot;</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>启动服务器。默认情况下，访问网址为： <a href="http://localhost:4000/">http://localhost:4000/</a><br><img src="https://s2.loli.net/2022/02/27/lik5gqQtrHKeLXp.png"></p><hr><h1 id="部署远端GitHub"><a href="#部署远端GitHub" class="headerlink" title="部署远端GitHub"></a>部署远端GitHub</h1><blockquote><p><strong>创建<a href="https://github.com/">GitHub</a>账号</strong></p></blockquote><blockquote><ol><li>新建GitHub仓库 <strong><code>New repository</code></strong></li><li><strong>用户部署个人博客的GitHub仓库的命名必须符合要求</strong></li><li><strong>库名：<code>name.github.io</code> 这里的 name 自己 Github 的 名子</strong></li><li><strong><code>Create-repository</code>创建仓库</strong></li></ol></blockquote><p><img src="/2022/03/10/hexo%E5%8D%9A%E5%AE%A2%E6%90%AD%E5%BB%BA/img/40f474d78e606b4993649a8181405cc.png"></p><h1 id="生成SSH添加到GitHub"><a href="#生成SSH添加到GitHub" class="headerlink" title="生成SSH添加到GitHub"></a>生成SSH添加到GitHub</h1><blockquote><p>生成SSH添加到GitHub，连接<code>GitHub</code>到本地<br><code>Git bash</code>中输入一下命令</p></blockquote><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">git config --global user.name <span class="string">&quot;输入你的GitHub用户名&quot;</span></span><br><span class="line">git config --global user.email <span class="string">&quot;输入你的GitHub的邮箱&quot;</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><blockquote><p>检查输入情况，使用以下两条命令</p></blockquote><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">git config --global user.name</span><br><span class="line">git config --global user.email</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h2 id="生成密钥"><a href="#生成密钥" class="headerlink" title="生成密钥"></a>生成密钥</h2><blockquote><p>执行命令生成密钥的过程需要确定四次</p></blockquote><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">ssh-keygen -t rsa -C <span class="string">&quot;你的邮箱&quot;</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>这时候生成了<code>.ssh</code>的文件夹。在<code>git bash</code>输入</p><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="built_in">cat</span> ~/.ssh/id_rsa.pub   <span class="string">&quot;复制id_rsa.pub 的文件内容&quot;</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>打开GitHub，点击用户头像&gt;<code>settings</code>&gt;<code>SSH and GPG keys</code>&gt;<code>New SSH kye</code>&gt;<code>Title</code>(可以随便取个名字)&gt;<code>key</code>(输入复制的密钥内容)<br><img src="/2022/03/10/hexo%E5%8D%9A%E5%AE%A2%E6%90%AD%E5%BB%BA/img/a0e34b1b31174c0f3fbba8685ba61fd.png"></p><ul><li><strong>在git bash输入<code>ssh -T git@github.com</code>，如果出现你的用户名，那就成功了。</strong></li></ul><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">ssh -T git@github.com</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><hr><h2 id="将hexo部署到GitHub上"><a href="#将hexo部署到GitHub上" class="headerlink" title="将hexo部署到GitHub上"></a>将hexo部署到GitHub上</h2><p>打开博客根目录下的<code>_config.yml</code>文件，这是博客的配置文件，在这里你可以修改与配置博客相关的各种信息<br>以下配置进行修改：</p><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">deploy:</span><br><span class="line">  <span class="built_in">type</span>: git</span><br><span class="line">  repo: git@github.com: https://github.com/LuckyZmj/LuckyZmj.github.io    <span class="string">&quot;你仓库地址&quot;</span></span><br><span class="line">  branch: master</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p><img src="https://s2.loli.net/2022/02/28/Hnk5dcfW6LMZXC4.png"></p><p>安装<code>deploy-git</code>，也就是部署的命令，这样你才能用命令部署到<code>GitHub</code>上。</p><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">npm install hexo-deployer-git --save</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">hexo clean    <span class="string">&quot;清除缓存文件&quot;</span></span><br><span class="line">hexo generate <span class="string">&quot;生成静态文件&quot;</span></span><br><span class="line">hexo deploy   <span class="string">&quot;部署网站&quot;</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>然后就可部署提交到<code>GitHub</code>，你的博客就成功了，可以在<a href="http://yourname.github.io/">http://yourname.github.io</a> 这个网站看到你的博客了,部署工作就完成了。</p><hr><h1 id="博客主题"><a href="#博客主题" class="headerlink" title="博客主题"></a>博客主题</h1><ul><li><strong><a href="https://hexo.io/themes/">hexo博客主题</a>【可以按自己需求选择主题】</strong></li></ul><ol><li><strong>在你hexo根目录<code>blog路径</code>下执行</strong></li></ol><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">地址：https://github.com/litten/hexo-theme-yilia</span><br><span class="line">下载 yilia 主题：</span><br><span class="line">git <span class="built_in">clone</span> https://github.com/litten/hexo-theme-yilia.git themes/yilia</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">地址：https://github.com/jerryc127/hexo-theme-butterfly</span><br><span class="line">下载 butterfly 主题：</span><br><span class="line">git <span class="built_in">clone</span> -b master https://github.com/jerryc127/hexo-theme-butterfly.git themes/butterfly</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><ul><li><strong>这里以<code>yilia</code>主题作为演示</strong></li></ul><ol start="2"><li><strong>应用主题</strong></li></ol><ul><li><strong>修改 Hexo 根目錄下的 <code>_config.yml</code>，把主題改為<code>yilia</code></strong></li></ul><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">theme: yilia</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><ul><li><strong>重启hexo博客</strong></li></ul><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">hexo cl (clean)    <span class="string">&quot;清除缓存文件&quot;</span></span><br><span class="line">hexo g (generate) <span class="string">&quot;生成静态文件&quot;</span></span><br><span class="line">hexo s (server)   <span class="string">&quot;启动服务&quot;</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p><img src="https://s1.ax1x.com/2022/03/14/bXjhf1.png" alt="bXjhf1.png"></p>]]></content>
      
      
      
